</code></pre>
This is running on a Mac with 10.10.1 and Xcode 6.1.1, compiled without optimizations. The offset value may need to be different on other architectures. With optimizations on, the approach may need to change. Don&#x27;t give me any guff about the conditions needed, since that&#x27;s the whole point of undefined behavior: it depends on context that should be irrelevant.<p>There&#x27;s no need to run it for 24 hours. Just run it, then pause in the debugger and step through a few loops. It&#x27;ll be evident that nothing changes.<p>If you need help getting it to work properly on your own setup, let me know.
